text: Once a Princess is a 2014 Filipino romantic drama movie directed by Laurice Guillen and was based on the novel of the same name by Angel Bautista. It stars Erich Gonzales, Enchong Dee, JC de Vera and was distributed by Star Cinema. == Other websites == * Category:2014 romantic drama movies Category:Filipino movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Laurice Guillen
